thread.title: Stephanie Umali

author: Stephanie Umali
title: Stephanie Umali
text: Overall, I am very satisfied with what I had received with this company. When I first came to the website I was really skeptical, because the price was cheap compared to other places where you would buy over-the-knee-boots. When I read through the reviews they were all so positive, so I decided to buy a pair for myself. It came in and let me tell you girls, I am SHOOK. So happy that I ordered from them! I could not be any happier. I would totally recommend, they have so many cute boots on here. I am definitely going to buy more shoes from here. It is definitely true to size & appearance. Girls, get yourself a pair before they run out in your size!
